{
  "doc_id": "43978",
  "text": "Studies were performed as previously described [CITATION_1] using 500 mg of nuclear extracts and polyclonal sera directed against P34 and P37 or polyclonal sera directed against the yeast L5 protein (formerly L1) [CITATION_2] . 1 mL of RNAseOUT (Invitrogen) was included in the precipitation reactions. Total RNA was isolated using TRIzol reagent (Invitrogen) and northern blot analysis was performed as before [CITATION_3] . Densitometric analysis was performed as above. Assays were performed in triplicate.",
